{"tid":1632662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"P牌仔玩依隻遊戲分享嘅後感！！！！","createTime":"2019-10-06T19:30:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T19:34:17.000Z","uid":314462,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c989b9aa9f31a85fd2b797f8fa17b182c60b8b4b","tid":1632662,"uid":314462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:30:51.000Z","msg":"話說依隻online game好危險，好多揸槍嘅有牌暴<br />\n<br />\n徒，依家好似警都唔警告就射，砰咗一聲之後突然<br />\n<br />\n佢後面有道力推咗一下，好彩有個背囊頂咗下。<br />\n<br />\n所以想講各位玩家後面一定要有一啲嘢for背對black <br />\n<br />\nobject 發癲時嘅保護手段。（被捉住果陣要金蟬脫殼，所以重要嘢放腰包/掛係前面嘅斜咩袋。）<br />\n<br />\n利申：發夢身歷其境姐嘛<br />\n<br />\n唔推都睇下，細微嘅位先重要，唔想再有手足有事！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （幫推都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb8aab3fadbe14f351fea313878140e404c29b6","tid":1632662,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:31:11.000Z","msg":"［分化收皮］香港01分化民陣失敗，聲稱裝修過火、民意逆轉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632454\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632454</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a2f33be5133460533ff6d9ee5b16b44026fefd2b","tid":1632662,"uid":314462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:31:25.000Z","msg":"唔望都睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53752c0f241c3536687ce48b0f2f9080ad0ba596","tid":1632662,"uid":314462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:32:18.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"dce2f9b0fe7f900e1936e0525971d6fbbe31df7f","tid":1632662,"uid":314462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:32:28.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"8d6063a2d34c338cc6c8be04d2713ccbdc27beaa","tid":1632662,"uid":314462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:32:38.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"3fbce702f90e440f7202